quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  15,45,Chisimu ŵaoga (wakun’jogopa Allah) tachiŵa m’Matimbe ga ku Mbepo ni sulo (syasichijilimaga chapasi pakwe)
  15,46,(Tachisalilidwa kuti) gajinjilani mwantendele n’di ŵagosedwa
  15,47,"Ni tuchityosya iwundo (ya uchimwa ni litima) yayaliji m’mitima mwao, tachiŵa (ŵakunonyelana) mwaulongo ali (atemi) pa itengu yauchimbichimbi mwakulolegana"
  15,48,"Ngagaja kwakwaya mwalakwemo masausyo galigose, soni ŵanganyao ngaaja koposyedwamo"
  15,49,"Mwatagulilani achikapolo Ŵangu yanti chisimu Une ni jwandi Jwakululuka kusyene, Jwachanasa channope"
  15,50,Soni kuti chisimu ilagasyo Yangu ni yaili ilagasyo yakupoteka nnope
  15,51,Soni mwatagulilani ya achalendo ŵa Ibrahima
  15,52,"Pandema jaŵajinjile kukwakwe ni kuŵecheta kuti: “Ntendele!” Jwalakwe (panyuma pakwajanga ni kwaona kuti ngakulya yakulya yajwaŵichile) jwatite: “Chisimu uwwe tukun’jogopa ŵanganyammwe.”"
  15,53,"Ŵanganyao ŵatite: “Nkajogopa! Chisimu uwwe tukumpa abali jakusengwasya janti chinkole mwanache jwakumanyilila nnope.”"
  15,54,"Jwalakwe jwatite: “Ana nkundagulila jele abali jakusengwasyaji kutendaga uchekulu uli ungwayiye kala? Ana abali jamboneji nkundagulila m’matalachi?”"
  15,55,"Ŵanganyao ŵatite: “Tukuntagulila abali jamboneji mwakuonaonape; basi ngasim’ba mwa ŵakata tama.”"
  15,56,"Jwalakwe jwatite: “Ana ninduni jwampaka akate tama kuchanasa cha Ambujegwe, pangaŵaga ŵakupotela?”"
  15,57,"(Kaneka) jwatite: “Abali jao (jine) jaichile nijapi jaomanja akutumidwa?”"
  15,58,"Ŵanganyao ŵatite: “Chisimu uwwe tutumisyidwe ku ŵandu ŵakuleŵa.”"
  15,59,"“Ikaŵeje ŵaliŵasa lya Lutwi, chisimu uwwe chitukajokole ŵanawose.”"
  15,60,"“Pangaŵanga ŵankwao, twapimichisye yanti ŵalakweo chaŵe mwa akusigalila munyuma (chajonanjidwe).”"